fields.label: Headline
fields.name: prvsn_to_ftr_headline

fields.label: Tracking Code
fields.name: tracking_code
fields.instructions: Paste your Google Analytics (or other) tracking code here. This will be added within HEAD tag. Please place code inside script tags <script></script>.

fields.label: Custom CSS
fields.name: custom_css
fields.instructions: Paste your Custom CSS code here. Any custom CSS entered here will override the theme CSS. In some cases, the !important tag may be needed.

fields.label: Head Scripts
fields.name: head_scripts
fields.instructions: Scripts will be placed within the HEAD tag. Please place code inside script tags <script></script>.

fields.label: Body Scripts
fields.name: body_scripts
fields.instructions: Scripts will be placed after the starting BODY tag. Please place code inside script tags <script></script>.
